<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= basePath %>/main.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>
  
  <div class="hero" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <h1>About Health Fitness Tracker</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;">
      Health Fitness Tracker is your personal companion for building a stronger, healthier version of yourself. 
      Whether you are training for a marathon, building muscle, or just staying active, we provide the tools you need to log your journey and visualize your consistency.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3 style="color: #2980b9; margin-top: 0;">üìù Seamless Tracking</h3>
      <p style="color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.6;">
        Log every session with precision. Record the duration, intensity, and specific type of workout. 
        Add personal notes to remember how you felt, what weights you lifted, or what goals you crushed that day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3 style="color: #27ae60; margin-top: 0;">üí° Smart Discovery</h3>
      <p style="color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.6;">
        Stuck in a rut? Our intelligent suggestion engine recommends exercises based on your chosen workout category. 
        Select 'Cardio', 'Strength', or 'Flexibility', and get instant inspiration for your next session.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3 style="color: #8e44ad; margin-top: 0;">üîç Deep Search</h3>
      <p style="color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.6;">
        Never lose track of your progress. Our powerful search allows you to filter your entire history by workout type, intensity, or keywords in your notes. 
        See exactly when you last trained a specific muscle group.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h3 style="color: #c0392b; margin-top: 0;">VX Secure & Private</h3>
      <p style="color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.6;">
        Your health data is personal. We use industry-standard encryption to ensure your account details and workout history remain private and secure.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 2rem;">
    <p style="color: #95a5a6;">
      Ready to start tracking? 
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a href="<%= basePath %>/workouts/add-workout" style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">Log a workout now</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="<%= basePath %>/register" style="color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">Create an account</a>
      <% } %>
    </p>
    <p style="color: #bdc3c7; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Health Fitness Tracker. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>